snippet.title: Atomic Society: Post-Apocalyptic City Builder With Moral Choices (Pre-Alpha Trailer 2016)
snippet.description:
Atomic Society an upcoming post-apocalyptic city building game that lets you sit in judgement and decide how society should be run. Pre-alpha available to try here:  http://www.farroadgames.com 

(All footage taken from an early development version.)
